<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM37.3">
<l>nātaṉai ñālamum vāṉamu mēttu naṟuntuḻāy</l>
<l>pōtaṉai poṉṉeṭuñ cakkarat tentai pirāṉṟaṉṉaip</l>
<l>pātam paṇiyaval lāraip paṇiyu mavarkaṇṭī</l>
<l>rōtum piṟappiṭai tōṟemmai yāḷuṭai yārkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The leader, the one with buds of fragrant Tulsi whom earth and heaven</l>
<l>praise, our father with the large golden discus, the lord,</l>
<l>they who humble themselves before those capable of humbling themselves at his feet, see,</l>
<l>possess us as servants in every birth we recite.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
